* Before you call

To verify your identity, you'll need
1. Social Insurance Number
2. Full name and date of birth
3. Your complete address
4. An assessed return, notice of assessment or reassessment, other tax document, or be signed in to My Account

If you are calling the CRA on behalf of someone else, you must be a legal representative.

* Telephone number

    1-800-959-8281

    Yukon, Northwest Territories and Nunavut:
    1-866-426-1527

    Outside Canada and the U.S. (operates in Eastern Time):
    613-940-8495

* Hours

Mon to Fri 	9 am to 9 pm
Sat		9 am to 5 pm
Sun		Closed
Closed on public holidays
